snippet.title: Interstellar Space: Genesis - Natural Law Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1419960/Interstellar_Space_Genesis__Natural_Law/

Natural Law, the first expansion to Interstellar Space: Genesis, features 2 new races, each fully equipped with unique new capabilities which are also usable by custom races. It also includes 9 new fully animated ruler options, 4 new music tracks, and 4 new leaders!
